name: Ultimate Kayne Game
description: Kanye’s new album Donda has dropped, and he is feeling more powerful than ever. He has finally grown into this person he has always meant to be. After his big tour, he thanks God for all that he has done for him. He realizes that he has made mistakes in the past and every day he does his best to right those wrongs. However, God tells him that if he truly wants peace, he must ascend to heaven to defeat the most powerful Kanye, which is old Kanye during the rise of his music career where he just released his 2016 album The Life of Pablo.
